ich he moved the German armies over into Austria in defiance of warn ings and threats and annexed that country prove him to be a man of power with whom the world has to reckon About five years ago when Hitlers Nazi party gained power in Germany that country was plunged into the depths of misery despair and humiliation It was subject to the military power of France its army was limited in num bers and it was without resources to defend itself against assault The country was in the depths of economic"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-04-27T17:42:36.216Z", "group": ["ndnp/vi", "library-of-virginia-richmond-va-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn94060041/1938-03-25/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:vi:batch_vi_doxa_ver01:data:sn94060041:00542866834:1938032501:0142/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=415&w=308", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:vi:batch_vi_doxa_ver01:data:sn94060041:00542866834:1938032501:0142/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=830&w=617", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/vi/batch_vi_doxa_ver01/data/sn94060041/00542866834/1938032501/0142.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["accomac", "virginia", "accomack", "united states"], "location_city": ["accomac"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["accomack"], "location_state": ["virginia"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["2", "0", "3", "0000000004", "6", "8", "sn94060041", "1", "4", "5"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn": ["sn94060041"], "number_page": ["0000000004"], "number_reel": ["0", "0", "5", "4", "2", "8", "6", "6", "8", "3", "4"], "online_format": ["image", "pdf", "online text"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["peninsula enterprise (accomac, va.) 1881-1965", "serial and 